---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

const currentDate = new Date().toLocaleDateString("en-US", {
    year: "numeric",
    month: "long",
    day: "numeric",
});
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
    <main
        class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 pt-40 pb-20 md:pt-48 md:pb-32 text-gray-300"
    >
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
            Privacy <span class="text-primary">Policy</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mb-12 text-sm text-gray-500">Last updated: {currentDate}</p>

        <div class="space-y-8 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
                At Logic & Lines, accessible from https://logicandlines.com, one
                of our main priorities is the privacy of our visitors. This
                Privacy Policy document contains types of information that is
                collected and recorded by Logic & Lines and how we use it.
            </p>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">
                    1. Information We Collect
                </h2>
                <p class="mb-4">
                    We may collect personal information in various ways,
                    including, but not limited to:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>
                        <strong class="text-white">Contact Data:</strong> Name, email
                        address, phone number.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong class="text-white">Navigation Data:</strong> IP address,
                        browser type, time spent on the site, and pages visited (via
                        cookies).
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong class="text-white">Form Data:</strong> Any information
                        you voluntarily provide when filling out a contact or subscription
                        form.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">
                    2. How We Use Your Information
                </h2>
                <p class="mb-4">We use the information we collect to:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>Operate and maintain our website.</li>
                    <li>Improve, personalize, and expand our website.</li>
                    <li>Understand and analyze how you use our site.</li>
                    <li>Develop new products, services, and features.</li>
                    <li>
                        Communicate with you (support, updates, or marketing
                        purposes if you have authorized it).
                    </li>
                    <li>Prevent fraud.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">
                    3. Cookies and Web Beacons
                </h2>
                <p class="mb-4">
                    Like any other website, Logic & Lines uses "cookies". These
                    are used to store information including visitors'
                    preferences, and the pages on the website that the visitor
                    accessed or visited. The information is used to optimize the
                    users' experience.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Additionally, we use tracking technologies such as <strong
                        class="text-white">Meta Pixel (Facebook)</strong
                    > and <strong class="text-white">Google Analytics</strong> to
                    analyze traffic and improve our advertising campaigns.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">
                    4. Third Parties and External Links
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Our Privacy Policy does not apply to other advertisers or
                    websites. Thus, we are advising you to consult the
                    respective Privacy Policies of these third-party ad servers
                    for more detailed information.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">
                    5. Data Protection Rights (GDPR / ARCO Rights)
                </h2>
                <p class="mb-4">
                    We want to ensure you are fully aware of all of your data
                    protection rights. Every user is entitled to the following:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>
                        <strong class="text-white">Access:</strong> Request copies
                        of your personal data.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong class="text-white">Rectification:</strong> Request
                        that we correct any information you believe is inaccurate.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong class="text-white">Erasure:</strong> Request that
                        we erase your personal data, under certain conditions.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong class="text-white">Objection:</strong> Object to processing
                        of your personal data.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">
                    6. Consent
                </h2>
                <p>
                    By using our website, you hereby consent to our Privacy
                    Policy and agree to its terms.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">
                    7. Contact
                </h2>
                <p class="mb-4">
                    If you have additional questions or require more information
                    about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us
                    through:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-none space-y-2">
                    <li>
                        <strong class="text-white">Email:</strong>
                        <a
                            href="mailto:logicandlinestudios@gmail.com"
                            class="text-[--color-primary] hover:underline"
                            >logicandlinestudios@gmail.com</a
                        >
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>
